---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"

import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro"
import TechnicalDivider from "../components/TechnicalDivider.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Joshua Jadulco"
  description="Technical profile - Full Stack Web Developer with expertise in Laravel, Vue, and modern web technologies"
>
  <main class="wrapper stack gap-12">
    <section class="stack gap-8">
      <Hero
        title="ABOUT_PROFILE"
        tagline="Technical profile - Background, experience, and technology stack analysis"
        align="start"
      />

      <div class="about-content stack gap-12">
        <div class="content-card">
          <TechnicalDivider title="BACKGROUND_PROFILE" />
          <div class="card-body stack gap-4">
            <p>
              I am a professional web developer with an Honours Bachelor of Technology in Software Development (Co-op).
              I have experience in full stack web development with expertise in Laravel, Vue, TailwindCSS,
              Bootstrap5, jQuery, JavaScript, TypeScript, and MySQL. I have developed web applications across
              Unix family (Debian, Ubuntu), macOS, and Windows operating systems.
            </p>
            <p>
              I specialize in advanced OOP design patterns including Repository, Factory, and Observer
              patterns for maintainable, testable code architecture. I have extensive experience with Laravel's
              ecosystem including Eloquent ORM, Laravel Queues with Redis drivers, Service Container
              dependency injection, and Middleware pipeline architecture. I implement comprehensive test
              suites using PHPUnit with mocking, feature tests, and database transactions for reliable
              continuous integration.
            </p>
            <p>
              I am proficient in DevOps with containerized environments using Docker for consistent development
              and deployment workflows. I automate CI/CD pipelines for testing, building, and deployment
              automation. I handle server management and configuration on Unix systems with Bash scripting for
              deployment automation, log rotation, and environment provisioning. I have experience with AWS
              services including EC2, S3, and RDS for scalable cloud infrastructure.
            </p>
            <p>
              My Laravel ecosystem expertise extends to Laravel Nova for admin interfaces, Laravel Scout
              for full-text search, Laravel Socialite for OAuth integrations, and Laravel Horizon for
              queue monitoring. I have a deep understanding of framework internals including Facade pattern
              implementation, service providers lifecycle, and request routing through the kernel.
              I optimize performance through query optimization, eager loading strategies, caching
              layers, and opcode caching configuration.
            </p>
            <p>
              I practice Test Driven Development (TDD) using the Red-Green-Refactor cycle, writing failing
              tests before implementing features. I use PHPUnit, Jest, and Vitest for comprehensive test
              coverage including unit tests, integration tests, and end-to-end testing with mocking and
              stubs for isolated testing. I integrate automated test execution into CI/CD pipelines for
              reliable continuous integration and delivery.
            </p>
            <p>
              I worked with Agile and Scrum methodologies including sprint planning, daily standups, sprint
              reviews, and retrospectives. I created user stories with clear acceptance criteria and managed
              sprint backlogs with velocity tracking. I collaborated effectively in cross-functional teams
              using Jira, Trello, and Azure DevOps for project tracking and continuous integration and
              continuous delivery workflows.
            </p>
            <p>
              I have experience with Waterfall SDLC for projects requiring sequential development phases
              with defined milestones. I perform requirements gathering and documentation, system design
              and architecture planning, formal testing and quality assurance stages, deployment planning
              and release management, and comprehensive maintenance and support documentation for enterprise
              software development lifecycle projects.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-card">
          <TechnicalDivider title="TECHNOLOGY_STACK" />
          <div class="tech-grid">
            <div class="tech-category">
              <h3 class="category-title">Front-End</h3>
              <div class="tech-tags">
                <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
